<doc f='qtbase-6.5.0/src/widgets/widgets/qabstractscrollarea.cpp' l='831'>/*!
    \since 4.6
    Sets \a margins around the scrolling area. This is useful for
    applications such as spreadsheets with &quot;locked&quot; rows and columns.
    The marginal space is is left blank; put widgets in the unused
    area.

    By default all margins are zero.
    \sa viewportMargins()
*/</doc>
